633
01:07:04,960 --> 01:07:10,800
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite li kinesku automobilsku industriju ulaganja u europsku proizvodnju kineskih automobila?

634
01:07:10,960 --> 01:07:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam puno.

635
01:07:12,639 --> 01:07:12,719
[SPEAKER_06] Hvala.

636
01:07:14,079 --> 01:07:15,519
