653
01:08:38,159 --> 01:08:39,920
[SPEAKER_06] Pojdimo na Megan.

654
01:08:40,159 --> 01:08:40,640
[SPEAKER_08] Da, sigurno.

655
01:08:40,960 --> 01:08:43,279
[SPEAKER_08] Dakle, ima li važnost odvajanje?

656
01:08:44,800 --> 01:08:51,600
